Dwarven_Plate_Armor_Male.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/44/SR-item-Dwarven_Plate_Armor_Male.jpg/300px-SR-item-Dwarven_Plate_Armor_Male.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/44/SR-item-Dwarven_Plate_Armor_Male.jpg/400px-SR-item-Dwarven_Plate_Armor_Male.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>A male <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nord\" title=\"Skyrim:Nord\">Nord</a> wearing dwarven plate armor\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"clear:both\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatright\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Dwarven_Mail\" title=\"Appears only with Alternative Armors - Dwarven Mail\"><img alt=\"Appears only with Alternative Armors - Dwarven Mail\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/37/SR-icon-armor-Dwarven_Mail_Helmet.png/32px-SR-icon-armor-Dwarven_Mail_Helmet.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/37/SR-icon-armor-Dwarven_Mail_Helmet.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Dwarven_Mail_Helmet.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/37/SR-icon-armor-Dwarven_Mail_Helmet.png/64px-SR-icon-armor-Dwarven_Mail_Helmet.png 2x\" /></a></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content1.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152051\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.025 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.074 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 756/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3242/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 901/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 931/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   39.969      1 -total\n 14.97%    5.983      3 Template:Weight_Icon\n 11.56%    4.620      3 Template:Icon_Base\n 10.89%    4.352      6 Template:Icon\n  7.62%    3.044      1 Template:CC\n  7.16%    2.861      1 Template:Mod_Note\n  7.12%    2.845      3 